		  <div class="shipping_lists">
			<ul>
			  <li>
				<p>Free Shipping is on all orders over $150.</p>
			  </li>
			  <li>
				<p>We offer delivery to the U.S. and International Shipping. Weekends and holidays are excluded. In-stock items only.</p>
			  </li>
			  <li>
				<p>Orders placed after 5pm PST will be processed the following business day.</p>
			  </li>
			  <li>
				<p>Orders placed on a weekend will be processed on the following Monday, holidays excluded.</p>
			  </li>
